name: Garden's Spirit
description:
"pruuuu?!"

"This sphinx was formed from the will and dreams of those who inhabited other lands, it then became the soul that gave life to the garden, protects and guides the plantz. Everyone in the garden understands their sacredness."


this work was created in the pixelpetz game by me (@eitaivan). i produced a series of original characters inspired by a magical garden, mixing references from ancient pagan cultures and fairy tales
